          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the steak is done, transfer to a plate and set aside to rest</p><p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat and add your <strong>gnocchi</strong> with a generous knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to crisp</p><p>Tip: Don’t stir too often as this will prevent the gnocchi from crisping!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-5-x700.jpg",
