            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms have softened, add your <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further or until evaporated</p><p>Once the balsamic vinegar has evaporated, remove the pan from the heat and add your <strong>spinach</strong>, mix it all together and<strong> </strong>set aside until slightly wilted – this is your <strong>balsamic mushrooms & spinach</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1775.-step-6-x400.jpg",
